What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Telepresence Robot Market?

Market Analysis and Insights:

Global Telepresence Robot Market

Telepresence robot market will grow at a CAGR of 15.65% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rising enhanced operational efficiency in enterprises due to virtual meeting is an essential factor driving the telepresence robot market.

A telepresence robot is also known as skype on wheels; it is the type of electronic device having wheels and is controlled by a remote which has wireless internet connectivity. These robots are remotely monitored autonomous robots and are equipped with a smartphone or motorized desktop stands that are connected to a camera or a monitor. The telepresence robot is assistive technology and can also be controlled by tablets, computers, or smartphones.

Rising demand from the healthcare industry is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also low cost due to availability of supporting devices, which in turn increases the demand for telepresence robot, rising improvement of operational efficacy in medical organizations due to technological advancements in telepresence robots and rising advancement in robotic technology and wide-level adoption from education to residential sectors, are the major factors among others boosting the telepresence robot market. Moreover, rising advancement in the robotic technology and wide level adoption from education and residential sectors and rising research and development activities in the market will further create new opportunities for telepresence robot market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, rising technical complexities leading to operational failures and increasing operating complications in telepresence robot are the major factors among others which will curtail the market growth, while rising lack of secure communication and common protocols will further challenge the telepresence robot market in the forecast period mentioned above.

